      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Perhaps to make fans feel better about this year’s cancellation, organizers have already announced Detroit Autorama 2022 will take place March 4-6. Michigan Hot Rod Association told fans on Facebook next year’s event will “be a knock out (sic).” This year could have been, 2-3 weeks afterward, but not in the way everyone would enjoy. Hopefully there isn’t another surge in COVID-19 just before those dates, otherwise gearheads might be looking at attending again in 2023.",
